[2669.578308, "o", "4\u001b[19;2H5\u001b[19;5H\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[30m\u001b[1m Make sure that the heap size is set to about half the memory available\u001b[20;2H\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[32m6\u001b[20;5H\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[30m\u001b[1m on the system and that the owner of the process is allowed to use this\u001b[21;2H\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[32m7\u001b[21;6H\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[30m\u001b[1mlimit.\u001b(B\u001b[m                                                                \u001b[22;2H\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[32m8\u001b[22;5H\u001b(B\u001b[m                                                                       \u001b[23;2H\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[32m9\u001b[23;6H\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[30m\u001b[1mElas\u001b[23;11Hicsearch performs poorly when the system is swapping the memory.\u001b[24;1H\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[32m50\u001b[25;1H51\u001b[25;6H\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[30m\u001b[1m----------------------------------\u001b[25;41HNetwork -----------------------------------\u001b[26;2H\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[32m2\u001b[27;2H3\u001b[27;6H\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[30m\u001b[1mBy default Elasticsearch is only acc\u001b[27;43Hssible on localhost. Set a different\u001b(B\u001b[m     \u001b[28;2H\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[32m4\u001b[28;5H\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[30m\u001b[1m address here to expose this node on the network:\u001b[29;2H\u001b(B\u001b[m\u001b[32m5\u001b[29;5H\u001b(B\u001b[m                                                                          \u001b"]
